## Objective: Identify and resolve cross-platform issues, document root causes, fixes, and regression test cases.

## Input: Error logs, network logs, reproduction steps.

## Output: /docs/DEBUG_REPORT.md, supplementary tests.

## Example Usage
```
/DEBUG 诊断 {{FEATURE}} 在 Android 真机崩溃问题，附复现脚本与最小复现实例。
/DEBUG  查找和诊断{{PROJECT}}中的全部问题，最后修复这些问题

```

## Key Points
- “Sandwich” Report: Phenomenon → Root Cause → Remediation
- Increase regression testing (unit/end-to-end)
